{"results":[{"aya":"015","id":4690,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"敬畏的人们必定在许多乐园中，在许多泉源畔，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"016","id":4691,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"接受他们的主所赏赐的。他们在生前确是行善的，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"017","id":4692,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"他们在夜间只稍稍睡一下，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"018","id":4693,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"他们在黎明时向主求饶，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"019","id":4694,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"他们的财产中，有乞丐和贫民的权利。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"020","id":4695,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"在大地上对于笃信的人们，有许多迹象；","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"021","id":4696,"locale":"zh","sura":"051","text":"在你们自身中也有许多迹象，难道你们看不见吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":9,"previousPage":"/zh/s051-2.json","nextPage":"/zh/s051-4.json"}}